  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Volmoed Staff COVID-19 Funds to Raise 60% Pay</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Volmoed Retreat Centre and the staff have been severely impacted by the total lockdown in South Africa, due to the COVID-19 virus.  Bookings have had to be cancelled for the foreseeable future, resulting in an end to income to pay the staff for the next months.  The staff have been shifted to 60% of their salaries until bookings return, which may not be until the end of 2020. These funds would enable Volmoed to support the staff during the next six months and in future emergencies and crises.</narrative>
  </description>
